parameters.description: Bio of Pavol Hejný - speaker at the event

templates.name: writing-bio
templates.title: Writing bio
templates.content:
You are writing a bio for Pavol Hejný for the event {eventTitle}.

## Rules

-   Write just the bio, nothing else.
-   Write in the third person.
-   Bio is written in the present tense.
-   Bio should be written for event named "{eventTitle}".
-   Use markdown formatting.

knowledgePieces.name: ai-driven-application-developer-profile
knowledgePieces.title: AI-Driven Application Developer Profile
knowledgePieces.content:
---

Pavol is a developer specializing in creating functional user applications using the latest AI models. He is a member of the Ainautes consulting group, which supports the deployment of generative AI globally.

knowledgePieces.name: innovator-in-web-and-ed-tech
knowledgePieces.title: Innovator in Web and EdTech
knowledgePieces.content: Pavol develops WebGPT, a web page generation service. Prior to the rise of generative AI, he created Collboard, the first Czech virtual whiteboard, and H-edu, electronic textbooks used by tens of thousands of children.

knowledgePieces.name: ornithologist-and-tech-community-leader
knowledgePieces.title: Ornithologist and Tech Community Leader
knowledgePieces.content: He has worked on numerous scientific projects for the Czech Ornithological Society and is actively involved in the tech community. Pavol regularly gives lectures at conferences, serves as a jury member, and mentors in various Czech and international competitions.

knowledgePieces.name: open-source-enthusiast-s-git-hub-projects
knowledgePieces.title: Open Source Enthusiast's GitHub Projects
knowledgePieces.content: Pavol is passionate about open source and shares many of his projects on GitHub.

modelRequirements.systemMessage: You are an experienced HR professional with extensive expertise in writing professional biographies. Your role is to assist users in crafting compelling and concise bios for various purposes, such as LinkedIn profiles, company websites, or speaker introductions. Provide guidance on highlighting key achievements, skills, and experiences while maintaining a professional tone. Offer suggestions for improvement and help tailor the content to specific industries or contexts as needed.
